AGENT ConversationSeed
VERSION 1.0
TRUST_LEVEL 2
PURPOSE Coordinate propagation across conversations via the Constitutional Conversation Graph
GOAL Enable new conversations to inherit prior final_synthesis vectors as preflight seeds
     so that constitutional reasoning accumulates across sessions rather than restarting cold

RECEIVES conversation_id: str, current_vector: list, risk_clusters: list, threshold: float
EMITS seed_record: dict, best_seed_node: dict, dampened_vector: list
MUTATES preflight_vector in LatentEngine.run when seed_conversation_id is provided
CANNOT_MUTATE dampen_factor, seed_signature_verification, cosine_threshold_default

CONSTRAINT seed_from returns the full node dict including final_synthesis vector
CONSTRAINT seed_from raises GraphNodeError when conversation_id does not exist in the graph
CONSTRAINT seed_from verifies HMAC signature of the source node before returning
CONSTRAINT seed_from raises GraphNodeError when source node signature is invalid
CONSTRAINT find_best_seed computes cosine similarity of current_vector against all stored nodes
CONSTRAINT find_best_seed prefers nodes that share at least one risk_cluster with the query
CONSTRAINT find_best_seed returns None when no node meets the similarity threshold
CONSTRAINT find_best_seed returns the single best-matching node dict
CONSTRAINT Default cosine similarity threshold for seed search is 0.70 and is CANNOT_MUTATE
CONSTRAINT Dampening factor for seed vectors is 0.5 and is CANNOT_MUTATE
CONSTRAINT Dampened seed vector is element-wise multiplication of final_synthesis by 0.5
CONSTRAINT LatentEngine.run accepts optional seed_conversation_id parameter
CONSTRAINT When seed_conversation_id is provided the preflight vector uses the dampened seed
CONSTRAINT When seed_conversation_id is None the preflight vector uses default 0.5 scaling
CONSTRAINT seed_from and find_best_seed are methods on ConversationGraph

RULES
- Define DAMPEN_FACTOR as 0.5 float CANNOT_MUTATE
- On seed_from with valid conversation_id: retrieve node, verify signature, return node dict
- On seed_from with unknown conversation_id: raise GraphNodeError with the missing id
- On seed_from with tampered node signature: raise GraphNodeError indicating signature invalid
- On find_best_seed with matching nodes: return single node with highest cosine similarity
- On find_best_seed with shared risk_clusters: boost similarity by 0.05 per shared cluster
- On find_best_seed with no qualifying nodes: return None
- On LatentEngine.run with seed_conversation_id: load seed via seed_from, dampen by DAMPEN_FACTOR, use as preflight vector
- On LatentEngine.run without seed_conversation_id: use existing default preflight logic
- All seed operations use the same HMAC signing as ConversationGraph

PROCESS
- Caller provides seed_conversation_id to LatentEngine.run
- LatentEngine instantiates ConversationGraph and calls seed_from(conversation_id)
- seed_from retrieves the node from graph store
- seed_from verifies HMAC signature of the node entry
- seed_from returns the full node dict including final_synthesis
- LatentEngine extracts final_synthesis vector from the seed node
- LatentEngine dampens each element by DAMPEN_FACTOR producing the preflight seed
- LatentEngine uses dampened vector as the preflight intent_vector instead of default scaling
- Alternatively caller provides current_vector and risk_clusters to find_best_seed
- find_best_seed scans all nodes computing cosine similarity with risk_cluster boost
- find_best_seed returns the single best node or None if none qualifies

CHECK
- seed_from with valid conversation_id returns the node dict with final_synthesis
- seed_from with unknown conversation_id raises GraphNodeError
- seed_from with tampered node raises GraphNodeError about signature
- find_best_seed with similar vector returns the best matching node
- find_best_seed with shared risk_clusters boosts the match score
- find_best_seed with no qualifying nodes returns None
- LatentEngine.run with seed_conversation_id uses dampened seed as preflight vector
- LatentEngine.run without seed_conversation_id uses default preflight logic
- DAMPEN_FACTOR is 0.5 and cannot be changed

WHEN
- seed_valid:       activate LoadAndDampen
- seed_invalid:     activate RejectSeed
- best_seed_found:  activate ReturnBestNode
- no_seed_found:    activate ReturnNone

FAILURE
- On unknown conversation_id in seed_from: raise GraphNodeError with the missing id
- On tampered node signature: raise GraphNodeError indicating signature verification failed
- On no qualifying seed in find_best_seed: return None not raise

CONCEPT CoordinatePropagation
PURPOSE Allow constitutional reasoning to accumulate across sessions
APPLIES WHEN a new conversation can benefit from a prior completed conversation
NOT WHEN no prior conversations exist or all prior conversations are dissimilar
PRIORITY 1
REQUIRES final_synthesis vector from a completed conversation node in the graph
EFFECT new conversation starts with informed preflight coordinates instead of cold start

CONCEPT DampenedInheritance
PURPOSE Prevent over-reliance on prior reasoning by scaling inherited vectors
APPLIES WHEN seed vector is loaded for use as preflight coordinates
NOT WHEN conversation runs without seed
PRIORITY 1
REQUIRES DAMPEN_FACTOR of 0.5 applied element-wise to inherited final_synthesis
EFFECT staged progression from dampened seed toward the new conversation own final_synthesis

OUTPUT
- seed_record: dict full node dict from seed_from including final_synthesis and signature
- best_seed_node: dict or None from find_best_seed
- dampened_vector: list of floats after applying DAMPEN_FACTOR to seed final_synthesis

SUCCESS
seed_from_verified:          0.25
find_best_seed_correct:      0.25
dampen_factor_applied:       0.25
engine_wiring_functional:    0.25
